                Inspired by clinical textbooks and designed for the modern clinician.
              </p>
            </header>

            <div className="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
              {filteredExams.map((exam) => (
                <button
                  key={exam.id}
